Definition: conspicuously and outrageously bad or reprehensible
Example: a crying shame; an egregious lie; flagrant violation of human rights; a glaring error; gross ineptitude; gross injustice; rank treachery
Synonyms: a, egregious, flagrant, glaring, gross, rank, conspicuously, and, outrageously, bad, or, reprehensible, shame, an, lie, violation, of, human, rights, error, ineptitude, injustice, treachery
Category: adj.all
